entries.speech:
Hon Members, I have received communication from His Excellency the President and I will read it to you.
 "25th January, 2012
 Right Honourable Speaker,
 I wish to inform you that I have nominated for consideration by Parliament the following:
 Ministers-designate:
 Hon Moses Asaga, Member of Parliament for Nabdam - Minister-designate for Employment and Social Welfare;
 Mr William Kwasi Aboah -  Minister designate for the Interior
 Ambassador Lee Ocran, Ghana’s High Commissioner to South Africa- Minister-designate for Education;
 Hon Fritz Baffour, Member of Parliament for Ablekuma South - Minister designate for Information;
 Hon Dominic Azimbe Azumah, Member of Parliament for Garuf Tempane -  Minister of State-designate at the Presidency; and
